{"tid":1956481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府官員對肺炎疫情樂觀認為「無咩嘢」 袁國勇：如同俗語所講「唔見棺材唔流眼淚」！","createTime":"2020-04-03T07:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T12:35:02.000Z","uid":63113,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea2556468cd7a96dc481f24993b02b5c61b127b","tid":1956481,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68938b9ed244c595148bc33ad74f43b93fd72e3c","tid":1956481,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"e5b68936063b4b048782788343cf602ae974724e","tid":1956481,"uid":257516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68938b9ed244c595148bc33ad74f43b93fd72e3c","tid":1956481,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"source?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"RTHK"},{"pid":"e6023b82a1962d59bf1fac54ff8de18ab797afb2","tid":1956481,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"唔見棺材唔流眼淚<br />\n但願係講班狗官中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2086ef591478b9feebb7c0c235cc5e06d65e616b","tid":1956481,"uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZpZC8WB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpZC8WB.png&h=f8a23724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身兼政府抗疫督導委員會專家顧問成員、港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇說，希望官員不要對新型肺炎疫情掉以輕心，他說，政府現時有些官員對疫情仍然好像很樂觀，覺得好像「無咩嘢」，他引述俗語所講「唔見棺材唔流眼淚」，強調疫情有如森林大、「唔係講玩」，他接受專訪時強調，每日有數十宗確診個案時已經要好緊張，否則很容易束手無策。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，有官員以為相比起外國，香港已做得好好，這是非常錯誤的想法，因為疫症可以好像海嘯般快到來。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇說，香港經歷過03年沙士，當年的爆發令所有公立醫院在很短時間內癱瘓，形容這種災難性狀態，港人歷歷在目，希望政府汲取沙士教訓，強調現在所做的事不足以令香港安全，香港必須再加強病毒檢測數量，繼續做好個人防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518681-20200403.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518681-20200403.htm&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=b27a4260\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518681-20200403.htm&h=94833a58\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518681-20200403.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bd906ae7d6c4f420e1e52354621187d2a969a2fc","tid":1956481,"uid":65091,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHgYTom.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHgYTom.gif&h=edc2a202&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00053f70f82e373f3eaa49d1e1c4dc04959d85a9","tid":1956481,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5b68936063b4b048782788343cf602ae974724e","tid":1956481,"uid":257516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68938b9ed244c595148bc33ad74f43b93fd72e3c","tid":1956481,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"source?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"RTHK"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:01:20.000Z","msg":"指有官員對疫情樂觀　袁國勇引俗語：唔見棺材唔流眼淚<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g1oTHgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg1oTHgG.png&h=1f4a9097&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abcc4340b575973b6e2089e6ba1bcd10f2495eb8","tid":1956481,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:02:57.000Z","msg":"感謝樓上po"},{"pid":"66682a13bffa5664e0eeacdb480e7a5f88dbeca2","tid":1956481,"uid":28818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:07:33.000Z","msg":"頭先見到已經有post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「解悶工廠」 點解還押抗爭者仲睇到連登？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1956428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1956428</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e665d1f1ae4e4c4b1b9bf38488d7e602d15b73ac","tid":1956481,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"車厘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d364058546193f3006d498ea06dd339b216c5429","tid":1956481,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:16:51.000Z","msg":"近幾日勇左好多 , 下下直線抽擊"},{"pid":"9929e4e02066cc5287ebf704219fd13284436b19","tid":1956481,"uid":182770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"D官員見到副棺材又唔係自己。所以咪樂觀面對"},{"pid":"a2ff84a0ea652af9fad1e45b2eecbdebc5ebc3b2","tid":1956481,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:19:46.000Z","msg":"班官見港人棺材只會愈睇愈開心<br />\n邊會流眼淚<br />\n無論死幾多<br />\n入返同等數量嘅內地磚才就完美解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad08732e3fb988ac24bd747ef7a6e928620492d","tid":1956481,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玩撚完"},{"pid":"38fe6b7bfe05eaa9bbb8c92b8673d45970ee1a91","tid":1956481,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"落棺"},{"pid":"43355d5738f856875b5b556034e549e9b85612c3","tid":1956481,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"一個許智勇，一個袁國勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a31d4b62e500ff31d4fc5a38b2683484a244bad","tid":1956481,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"因為政府內部存在大量官狀病毒"},{"pid":"5c556e83c9fbc2f5178291a0ffb309810c2c16f3","tid":1956481,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0